---
<section id="services" class="services-section">
  <h2>Services</h2>
  <div class="services-list">
    <div class="service-item reveal" data-delay="0">
      <img src="/icons/consult.svg" class="icon" alt="">
      <h3>Clinical AI Consulting</h3>
      <p>Bridging clinical practice and AI implementation. Wearable data pipelines, autonomic monitoring systems, patient-reported outcomes integration. Built and validated in real clinical contexts. Available remotely worldwide.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="service-item reveal" data-delay="100">
      <img src="/icons/biomech.svg" class="icon" alt="">
      <h3>Autonomic & Biomechanical Assessment</h3>
      <p>10+ years of clinical osteopathy and biomechanics. HRV-guided load management, post-infectious fatigue protocols, movement analysis. Evidence-based, measurable outcomes. Available remotely worldwide.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="service-item reveal" data-delay="200">
      <img src="/icons/neuro.svg" class="icon" alt="">
      <h3>AI Model Evaluation (Healthcare)</h3>
      <p>LLM evaluation for clinical applications — safety, accuracy, and reasoning quality. Active evaluator for Anthropic/Outlier. Domain expertise in medical context and edge cases. Available remotely worldwide.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .services-section {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    background: #F7FCFB;
  }

  .services-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: #223;
  }

  .services-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .service-item {
    flex: 1 1 250px;
    background: #FFFFFFEE;
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .service-item .icon {
    width: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .service-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #334;
  }

  .service-item p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #556;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .service-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }
</style>
